=========
CHANGELOG
=========

0.7.0 (2023-07-10)
==================

- Django 4 compatibility
- Removed Django (1.11,2.2/3.0/3.1) compatibility
- Moved CI/CD to Github Actions

0.6.2 (2020-07-23)
==================

- Set default value to [] in MultiEmailField


0.6.1 (2020-02-05)
==================

- Remove six dependency


0.6.0 (2020-02-05)
==================

- Django (2.2/3.0) compatibility


